OL,3,CCouncil granted interim injunction
OL,4,Cover pickets in Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council has been
OL,7,Fgranted an interim injunction to
OL,8,Fensure that picketing and protests at
OL,9,Fits three depots is in accordance with
OL,10,Flegal provisions.
OL,12,FThe council said the injunction, which
OL,13,Fis in place until Thursday when a
OL,14,Ffurther hearing will take place, sets
OL,15,Fout expected behaviour from pickets
OL,16,Fand aims to prevent the obstruction of
OL,17,Fvehicles leaving the depots.
