OL,3,CCouncil granted interim injunction
OL,4,Cover pickets in Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FMembers of Unite have been on all-out
OL,7,Fstrike since March 11th in a row over
OL,8,Fpay and jobs, leading to bags of
OL,9,Frefuse piling up across the city.
OL,11,FThe council said: "The council must
OL,12,Fnow work to resume weekly collections
OL,13,Fand reduce the recent build-up of
OL,14,Fwaste experienced in the city.
OL,16,F"Our priority is to deliver a reliable
OL,17,Fwaste service to the people of
OL,18,FBirmingham.
