OL,3,CCouncil granted interim injunction
OL,4,Cover pickets in Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,F"We have seen an increase in
OL,7,Fdisruption at our depots, with workers
OL,8,Fand vehicles being prevented from
OL,9,Fdoing their jobs. This has in turn led
OL,10,Fto a backlog of approximately 12,800
OL,11,Ftonnes of waste on the streets.
OL,13,F"The council has been negotiating with
OL,14,FUnite since the start of this strike
OL,15,Faround the behaviours we have seen at
OL,16,Four depots, and whilst everyone has a
OL,17,Fright to protest, the council has a
OL,18,Fpublic health duty to uphold and
OL,19,Fclearing waste is central to this.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
