OL,3,CCouncil granted interim injunction
OL,4,Cover pickets in Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,F"We believe that these actions are in
OL,7,Fbreach of the law. As a result, the
OL,8,Fcouncil issued Unite's lawyers with a
OL,9,Fletter before action at the start of
OL,10,Fthe week. We were subsequently given
OL,11,Fassurances in writing that there would
OL,12,Fbe a change at the depots.
OL,14,F"This has not happened and they have
OL,15,Fbreached those reassurances this
OL,16,Fmorning by again not allowing our
OL,17,Ftrucks to leave.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
