OL,3,CCouncil granted interim injunction
OL,4,Cover pickets in Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,F"Therefore, the council has taken the
OL,7,Fdecision to proceed with an
OL,8,Fapplication to the High Court for a
OL,9,Flegal injunction to restrict the
OL,10,Funlawful behaviour. This is not
OL,11,Fsomething we wanted to do and have
OL,12,Fgiven Unite many opportunities to co-
OL,13,Foperate with us and avoid this course
OL,14,Fof action.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
