OL,3,CCouncil granted interim injunction
OL,4,Cover pickets in Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,F"The health and safety of the people
OL,7,Fof Birmingham is vitally important and
OL,8,Fthe council has been forced to take
OL,9,Fthis action to prevent waste
OL,10,Faccumulating across our city,
OL,11,Fimpacting deprived communities the
OL,12,Fmost."
OL,14,FUnite said it will continue to conduct
OL,15,Fa lawful and peaceful picket and it's
OL,16,Fregrettable that the council has
OL,17,Fchosen to take legal action.
